WEBVTT

01:27.680 --> 01:35.030
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.430 --> 01:37.890
[Episode 2]

01:50.039 --> 01:53.110
[Capital Film Studio]

01:58.390 --> 02:04.320
[Capital Film Studio]

02:16.610 --> 02:17.150
Comrade,

02:17.310 --> 02:18.640
who are you looking for?

02:18.710 --> 02:21.020
Hello, sir. I'm looking for Director Weng.

02:21.020 --> 02:23.280
Director Weng? What do you want with him?

02:23.310 --> 02:24.640
I'm sort of his student.

02:25.250 --> 02:26.400
From the Central Academy of Drama?

02:26.400 --> 02:26.780
Or the Beijing Film Academy?

02:26.780 --> 02:28.900
No, no, no.
I wasn't professionally trained.

02:28.900 --> 02:29.860
I'm from Yantai.

02:30.430 --> 02:31.680
I'm a playwriting enthusiast.

02:31.680 --> 02:32.560
My name is Xu Shengli.

02:32.560 --> 02:33.340
Xu, spelled X-U.

02:33.340 --> 02:34.410
Shengli as in "Shengli Oilfield."

02:34.410 --> 02:34.740
I see.

02:34.810 --> 02:35.620
Director Weng's student, right?

02:35.620 --> 02:36.020
Come on.

02:36.020 --> 02:36.930
Come on in. Let's talk.

02:36.930 --> 02:38.920
[Studio]

02:38.840 --> 02:40.100
At the end of last year,

02:40.180 --> 02:41.250
Director Weng came to our factory

02:41.250 --> 02:43.500
to experience life
at the grassroots level.

02:43.500 --> 02:44.340
I served

02:45.310 --> 02:46.620
as a worker representative

02:46.620 --> 02:48.020
to assist Director Weng.

02:48.340 --> 02:49.590
For that week or so,

02:50.130 --> 02:52.000
we kept talking and communicating.

02:52.000 --> 02:53.740
Director Weng even praised me and said

02:53.740 --> 02:54.670
I had potential,

02:54.680 --> 02:56.010
and I must keep writing.

02:56.430 --> 02:57.750
He asked me to send the script to him

02:57.750 --> 02:58.810
once I finished it.

02:59.030 --> 03:00.190
He said he'd show the script

03:00.190 --> 03:01.390
to the other experts.

03:01.470 --> 03:02.780
He said if it was good,

03:02.930 --> 03:04.330
it might even get filmed.

03:04.740 --> 03:06.400
Now that my script is done,

03:06.740 --> 03:07.620
I thought I'd come personally

03:07.620 --> 03:08.800
to visit Director Weng

03:08.800 --> 03:10.460
and also pay a visit to you all.

03:13.580 --> 03:14.500
Did you mail it?

03:15.410 --> 03:15.800
I did.

03:16.130 --> 03:16.620
Zou,

03:17.060 --> 03:17.910
look for it.

03:19.960 --> 03:20.590
Young man.

03:21.650 --> 03:22.630
That script of yours,

03:22.630 --> 03:23.620
what's it called?

03:23.620 --> 03:24.280
It's called

03:24.460 --> 03:25.630
"As High as the Sky."

03:31.200 --> 03:32.329
["As High as the Sky"
Author: Xu Shengli]

03:33.520 --> 03:34.120
Young man,

03:34.430 --> 03:35.360
look at our workload.

03:35.090 --> 03:36.160
["As High as the Sky"
Author: Xu Shengli]

03:35.380 --> 03:37.040
We're under so much pressure.

03:38.930 --> 03:39.530
It's fine!

03:39.710 --> 03:40.970
Don't bother looking for it.

03:40.970 --> 03:42.100
I brought a new copy.

03:45.000 --> 03:46.400
I hope you can take a look

03:46.530 --> 03:47.780
and give me some advice.

03:47.780 --> 03:48.150
Okay.

03:48.870 --> 03:50.329
Director Weng isn't here.

03:50.340 --> 03:50.970
I can't tell you

03:50.970 --> 03:51.840
where he went.

03:52.370 --> 03:53.250
Our studio is

03:53.300 --> 03:54.280
mainly for creative work.

03:54.280 --> 03:54.910
You know,

03:55.079 --> 03:56.410
we hate interruptions.

03:56.530 --> 03:57.280
When you go back,

03:57.280 --> 03:58.650
contact Director Weng first.

03:58.650 --> 03:59.740
Come again after you reach him.

03:59.740 --> 04:00.070
Okay?

04:00.690 --> 04:01.750
Yes, I got it.

04:02.240 --> 04:04.100
Well... I'll come back next time.

04:04.430 --> 04:05.620
See you around.

04:11.370 --> 04:12.900
Sir, may I ask your surname?

04:13.740 --> 04:14.870
Me? My surname is Wu.

04:15.020 --> 04:15.470
Mr. Wu.

04:16.769 --> 04:17.870
My name is Xu Shengli.

04:17.870 --> 04:18.660
I know.

04:18.660 --> 04:19.920
You already said that.

04:20.769 --> 04:21.630
Alright, then,

04:21.930 --> 04:23.130
I will leave you to it.

04:31.500 --> 04:33.180
When did Director Weng take on

04:33.240 --> 04:34.440
such a tacky student?

04:34.770 --> 04:35.860
Then why didn't you tell him

04:35.860 --> 04:36.890
that Director Weng is on a business trip?

04:36.320 --> 04:39.390
[Movie script: "As High as the Sky"
Author: Xu Shengli]

04:37.370 --> 04:38.040
This guy,

04:38.240 --> 04:39.240
from what I can see,

04:39.240 --> 04:40.500
doesn't even have Director Weng's number

04:40.500 --> 04:41.010
to reach him,

04:41.010 --> 04:42.210
and he just came here like that.

04:42.210 --> 04:43.610
I wouldn't dare tell him.

04:43.920 --> 04:45.580
What he said might not be true.

04:45.740 --> 04:46.260
Wu,

04:46.510 --> 04:47.810
so you chatted with him for so long

04:47.810 --> 04:48.870
just for material?

04:50.060 --> 04:51.450
Gathering this kind of material is

04:51.450 --> 04:52.780
completely worthless.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.300
He is just a nobody.

04:54.980 --> 04:56.000
I agree.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.250
The sleep I got last night

05:01.920 --> 05:03.320
felt like fighting a war.

05:03.430 --> 05:05.160
I didn't sleep a wink all night.

05:05.630 --> 05:06.350
That jerk

05:06.380 --> 05:07.780
really messed things up.

05:07.950 --> 05:09.040
My half-day's pay...

05:09.040 --> 05:10.620
I just slept right through it.

05:10.620 --> 05:11.390
What kind of place is this

05:11.390 --> 05:12.850
that you've brought me to?

05:14.860 --> 05:15.920
I told you

05:15.950 --> 05:17.100
I wanted a single room upstairs.

05:17.100 --> 05:18.960
I don't want to live in a basement.

05:27.860 --> 05:28.680
Yeah.

05:28.950 --> 05:31.010
But the rooms upstairs are full.

05:31.390 --> 05:32.360
Since you're already here,

05:32.360 --> 05:33.430
let me show you around.

05:33.430 --> 05:34.190
You need to shop around

05:34.190 --> 05:35.680
even when buying something.

05:35.680 --> 05:36.540
Where did you go?

05:36.540 --> 05:37.770
He saw a pretty girl.

05:37.810 --> 05:39.270
The big peacock wants to strut his stuff.

05:39.270 --> 05:40.470
This is the washroom.

05:40.980 --> 05:41.870
The hot water room is over here,

05:41.870 --> 05:43.920
offering hot water around the clock.

05:43.920 --> 05:45.620
-The four directions...
-I'm heading out for jobs.

05:45.620 --> 05:46.750
Help me take my stuff back.

05:46.750 --> 05:47.640
Take care, bro.

05:48.659 --> 05:49.430
Have you ever seen a basement

05:49.430 --> 05:50.830
with such good sunlight?

05:51.370 --> 05:52.060
The sun also shines

05:52.060 --> 05:53.659
over there in the afternoon.

05:53.980 --> 05:54.740
Twice a day.

05:55.430 --> 05:56.040
My place is rated

05:56.040 --> 05:57.220
a hygiene model every year

05:57.220 --> 05:59.270
with high tenant satisfaction.

06:38.810 --> 06:39.550
Artist.

06:39.830 --> 06:41.330
Hello, my name is Tao Liangliang.

06:41.330 --> 06:42.260
Are you new here?

06:42.420 --> 06:44.330
H-Hurry up and take me

06:44.420 --> 06:45.480
to see that room.

06:46.420 --> 06:46.950
This way.

06:47.920 --> 06:48.810
There used to be

06:49.120 --> 06:50.630
a student taking the dance academy exam.

06:50.630 --> 06:52.400
The mother and daughter
just moved out this morning,

06:52.210 --> 06:54.400
[Warning: No trash in the corridors.]

06:52.480 --> 06:53.480
and then you came.

06:53.480 --> 06:53.940
Tell me,

06:54.240 --> 06:54.730
doesn't it

06:54.400 --> 06:57.400
[Please walk and speak quietly.]

06:54.810 --> 06:56.810
feel like this room is meant for you?

06:57.630 --> 06:58.680
Come in, please.

06:59.750 --> 07:00.810
Take a look around.

07:00.950 --> 07:02.550
It's a single room, isn't it?

07:10.770 --> 07:12.680
I don't have many female guests here.

07:12.680 --> 07:14.510
You pay for one bed

07:14.620 --> 07:16.130
but get a private room.

07:18.820 --> 07:20.480
So, how much is it a day?

07:20.570 --> 07:21.890
Eight. Just 8.

07:26.740 --> 07:28.760
You make it sound nice,

07:28.810 --> 07:29.720
but looking at it,

07:29.720 --> 07:31.050
it's nothing special.

07:31.130 --> 07:32.220
It's all dirty.

07:32.770 --> 07:33.800
The mother and daughter

07:33.800 --> 07:35.070
left in a hurry this morning.

07:35.070 --> 07:35.860
I haven't had time

07:35.860 --> 07:36.659
to clean up yet.

07:36.659 --> 07:37.740
It looks a bit messy.

07:37.740 --> 07:38.430
Before,

07:38.480 --> 07:38.980
they used

07:38.980 --> 07:40.580
their own sheets and covers.

07:40.890 --> 07:41.890
They kept the room

07:42.060 --> 07:43.100
super neat.

07:43.540 --> 07:44.159
Besides,

07:44.450 --> 07:46.580
if you're going to act in the future...

07:47.690 --> 07:49.180
Are you an actress, miss?

07:49.450 --> 07:50.500
That's perfect!

07:50.740 --> 07:51.720
People living in this building are

07:51.720 --> 07:53.050
all engaged in the arts.

07:53.390 --> 07:54.440
There's an actor

07:54.750 --> 07:55.510
in our room.

07:55.510 --> 07:55.830
Yes.

07:56.560 --> 07:57.870
There are also

07:58.070 --> 07:58.810
a dancer,

07:59.370 --> 08:00.410
a singer,

08:00.800 --> 08:01.570
and a screenwriter.

08:01.570 --> 08:02.970
And I play the saxophone.

08:03.070 --> 08:05.010
This kind of artistic atmosphere is

08:05.010 --> 08:05.870
hard to come by.

08:06.370 --> 08:07.300
Exactly.

08:07.750 --> 08:08.480
Our place,

08:08.870 --> 08:10.830
small as it is, has everything.

08:11.250 --> 08:12.450
It gets a motley crew.

08:12.540 --> 08:13.200
Look at him,

08:13.620 --> 08:15.120
he's not just a saxophone player,

08:15.120 --> 08:15.740
an artist.

08:16.310 --> 08:16.840
He's also

08:17.250 --> 08:18.070
a Beijinger,

08:18.740 --> 08:19.680
a local.

08:20.450 --> 08:21.660
You can ask him anything

08:21.660 --> 08:22.520
about Beijing.

08:23.860 --> 08:25.060
You're from Beijing?

08:25.310 --> 08:26.240
Why are you, a local,

08:26.240 --> 08:27.860
staying in a hostel?

08:28.450 --> 08:29.450
A-Are you two

08:29.450 --> 08:30.810
ganging up to trick me?

08:31.060 --> 08:31.430
No.

08:31.620 --> 08:33.250
Even a local lives here.

08:33.659 --> 08:35.870
That just proves how great this place is.

08:35.870 --> 08:37.669
I don't stay at home. I live here.

08:37.669 --> 08:39.240
This place is even better than home!

08:39.240 --> 08:40.789
Besides, we Beijingers

08:40.789 --> 08:41.940
never trick outsiders.

08:41.940 --> 08:42.470
We don't.

08:42.500 --> 08:43.460
Just stay here.

08:43.630 --> 08:44.360
Listen to me.

08:44.580 --> 08:45.390
It's perfect.

08:45.860 --> 08:47.750
Girl, just stay here.

08:47.790 --> 08:49.150
It's absolutely perfect.

08:49.150 --> 08:49.940
Don't hesitate.

08:49.940 --> 08:51.790
Otherwise, this room will be booked
by this afternoon.

08:51.790 --> 08:53.250
My hostel is very popular.

08:54.410 --> 08:54.960
Well,

08:55.410 --> 08:56.600
if any rooms upstairs

08:56.600 --> 08:57.620
become available,

08:57.620 --> 08:59.480
you must let me know immediately.

09:02.530 --> 09:03.360
What did I tell you?

09:03.360 --> 09:05.220
You'd definitely like this room.

09:05.530 --> 09:06.580
So, what now?

09:07.410 --> 09:09.860
Then I'll just stay here temporarily

09:09.890 --> 09:11.350
and make do with it for now.

09:11.630 --> 09:12.510
Alright!

09:12.890 --> 09:14.250
Put your luggage down, please.

09:14.250 --> 09:15.980
We'll go up and register later.

09:16.210 --> 09:17.390
Hey, Mr. Tao.

09:17.480 --> 09:18.370
Can you sort out the furniture

09:18.370 --> 09:19.150
and other stuff?

09:19.150 --> 09:20.320
Leave it to me. Hurry up.

09:20.320 --> 09:22.450
If you need anything, just turn to him.

09:25.870 --> 09:26.200
Miss,

09:26.530 --> 09:27.730
which bed do you want?

09:28.390 --> 09:30.550
See if you want this side

09:30.550 --> 09:31.360
or that side.

09:31.630 --> 09:32.340
This side is

09:33.200 --> 09:33.750
quiet.

09:34.500 --> 09:35.410
And here,

09:35.940 --> 09:38.220
it's sunny and airy.

09:38.770 --> 09:40.460
Anyway, both have their pros.

09:47.220 --> 09:48.550
I've watched your show.

09:49.750 --> 09:51.080
You just recognized me?

09:51.100 --> 09:52.360
A Republic-era drama.

09:53.320 --> 09:54.840
A wealthy young lady!

09:56.600 --> 09:57.480
So pretty!

09:58.510 --> 10:01.170
It's just
that you were unreasonably ferocious

10:01.200 --> 10:02.130
when you got angry.

10:02.130 --> 10:03.600
You looked pretty wild.

10:04.390 --> 10:04.940
But I think you...

10:04.940 --> 10:06.550
You're quite young,

10:06.650 --> 10:07.770
but you went blind early.

10:07.770 --> 10:08.260
Get out.

10:08.530 --> 10:09.600
-Get out! Go!
-Wait, I...

10:09.600 --> 10:10.530
I don't need your help.

10:10.530 --> 10:11.510
Go away.

10:11.600 --> 10:13.320
-Just leave.
-I'm briefly sharing

10:13.320 --> 10:14.650
my thoughts on the show.

10:19.910 --> 10:20.710
My saxophone.

10:22.500 --> 10:24.100
Tell me if you need anything.

10:25.930 --> 10:27.260
She's totally spoiled.

10:28.940 --> 10:30.510
Once she's worked up,

10:31.700 --> 10:32.700
she's ferocious,

10:32.960 --> 10:33.890
running so wild.

10:40.270 --> 10:49.930
[Welcome to Beijing]

10:50.000 --> 10:53.650
[No entry for vehicles.]

10:58.100 --> 11:03.220
[Welcome to Beijing]

11:07.740 --> 11:08.310
Sir!

11:08.750 --> 11:09.230
Sir.

11:10.550 --> 11:11.840
Why are you squatting here?

11:11.840 --> 11:13.060
I've been looking for you for a while.

11:13.060 --> 11:17.930
[No entry for vehicles.]

11:13.750 --> 11:15.410
I thought you weren't coming.

11:16.210 --> 11:17.390
I did have something to handle
this afternoon.

11:17.390 --> 11:18.120
I got held up.

11:19.150 --> 11:19.880
Here you are.

11:20.770 --> 11:21.830
You found your bag?

11:23.440 --> 11:25.300
Then where did you get this money?

11:25.580 --> 11:26.650
I said I'd pay you back.

11:26.650 --> 11:27.850
So I definitely will.

11:27.860 --> 11:28.360
Take it.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.790
But this is too much.

11:36.410 --> 11:38.210
That's 20 extra for just one day.

11:38.720 --> 11:40.010
I'm not a loan shark.

11:40.080 --> 11:40.940
Take this back.

11:41.980 --> 11:42.780
Just take it.

11:42.840 --> 11:44.240
You did me a big favor yesterday.

11:44.240 --> 11:45.720
No need. Fifty is enough.

11:45.770 --> 11:46.230
Keep it.

11:47.940 --> 11:49.130
Just take it.

11:49.290 --> 11:49.620
Wait.

11:53.200 --> 11:53.730
I'm fine.

11:57.010 --> 11:58.080
Forget about the money.

11:58.080 --> 11:58.880
Lean here now.

12:02.410 --> 12:03.560
What's up with you?

12:04.360 --> 12:05.000
It's nothing.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.600
I just haven't eaten all day.

12:09.700 --> 12:10.370
Thank you.

12:16.740 --> 12:18.740
How are you feeling? Any better now?

12:20.030 --> 12:20.620
Sorry,

12:20.670 --> 12:22.330
I haven't had any food all day.

12:24.740 --> 12:25.600
Eat these buns.

12:27.290 --> 12:28.030
You have some, too.

12:28.030 --> 12:29.160
I've already eaten.

12:31.010 --> 12:32.130
What is wrong with you?

12:32.130 --> 12:33.990
You got money, but you didn't eat.

12:37.290 --> 12:39.350
Well... Where did you get that money?

12:40.240 --> 12:42.170
Don't worry. I didn't steal or rob.

12:43.340 --> 12:45.890
I didn't use the money you gave me
to stay in a hotel either.

12:45.890 --> 12:47.650
During the day, I handed out flyers

12:47.650 --> 12:48.980
and earned 10 yuan a day.

12:49.770 --> 12:50.570
Just a second.

12:56.130 --> 12:57.150
Last night, I was sorting books

12:57.150 --> 12:58.380
together with them.

12:58.480 --> 13:00.080
That was 8 yuan for 100 books.

13:00.370 --> 13:03.230
I didn't mean to skip meals.
I just didn't have time.

13:07.740 --> 13:08.940
You're pretty tough.

13:09.630 --> 13:10.550
Eat this egg.

13:12.370 --> 13:13.770
But you still need to eat.

13:13.860 --> 13:15.120
Making money can wait.

13:18.600 --> 13:19.460
By the way, sir,

13:20.000 --> 13:21.260
have you settled down?

13:21.820 --> 13:23.120
I'd like to ask you something.

13:23.120 --> 13:24.010
The small hotel I found is

13:24.010 --> 13:25.200
quite convenient,

13:25.790 --> 13:27.500
but it costs over 10 yuan a day.

13:27.620 --> 13:29.020
I really can't afford it.

13:29.890 --> 13:30.770
I don't even know where to get

13:30.770 --> 13:32.340
the money for my lesson fees.

13:32.340 --> 13:33.580
W-What lesson fees?

13:33.840 --> 13:34.700
Vocal lessons.

13:34.890 --> 13:36.420
That's 100 yuan per lesson.

13:37.010 --> 13:37.750
One hundred?

13:38.620 --> 13:39.480
That is so expensive.

13:39.480 --> 13:40.440
It's not expensive.

13:40.440 --> 13:41.370
Private vocal lessons nowadays

13:41.370 --> 13:42.430
all cost this much.

13:49.120 --> 13:50.480
Do you have any recommendations?

13:50.480 --> 13:51.940
I mean a safe place to stay.

13:52.270 --> 13:53.100
M-My place.

13:54.790 --> 13:55.270
Not my place.

13:55.270 --> 13:56.150
Well... It is my place.

13:56.150 --> 13:58.250
I mean the hotel I'm staying at.

13:58.620 --> 13:59.720
That is pretty good.

13:59.720 --> 14:01.130
It's in an alley and quite safe.

14:01.130 --> 14:02.820
Most importantly, it's cheap.

14:02.820 --> 14:03.580
How much?

14:04.360 --> 14:06.120
My bed is 6 yuan a day.

14:07.700 --> 14:09.410
Okay, I'll go right now.

14:10.420 --> 14:11.290
Don't rush to decide.

14:11.290 --> 14:12.170
Go take a look first.

14:12.170 --> 14:13.500
Decide after you see it.

14:14.390 --> 14:15.340
I think

14:16.000 --> 14:17.320
the basic living conditions

14:17.320 --> 14:18.580
must've been secured.

14:21.940 --> 14:22.340
Okay.

14:25.550 --> 14:26.150
By the way,

14:26.370 --> 14:27.510
how should I address you?

14:27.510 --> 14:28.170
Xu Shengli.

14:28.600 --> 14:29.500
Xu, spelled X-U.

14:29.500 --> 14:32.030
-Shengli
-Shengli as in "Shengli Oilfield."

14:33.360 --> 14:33.760
Right.

14:34.840 --> 14:35.480
Eat up now.

14:35.860 --> 14:37.480
I'll take you there to have a look
after you finish.

14:37.480 --> 14:37.910
Okay.

14:38.360 --> 14:40.160
I won't stand on ceremony, then.

14:43.940 --> 14:45.120
Sir, you're so nice.

14:53.530 --> 14:54.620
Is it really okay?

14:54.730 --> 14:55.590
No worries!

14:56.080 --> 14:57.360
Should I get down?

14:57.460 --> 14:59.140
No need. It's still a ways off.

14:59.460 --> 15:00.590
There's no problem.

15:00.750 --> 15:01.220
Okay.

15:03.580 --> 15:04.180
It's fine.

15:05.130 --> 15:05.610
Look.

15:06.000 --> 15:07.400
This is the Corner Tower.

15:07.620 --> 15:08.840
When I came to Beijing before,

15:08.840 --> 15:09.840
I visited it once.

15:10.060 --> 15:11.660
Oh, you've been here before?

15:17.080 --> 15:17.740
Here we are.

15:18.360 --> 15:19.130
Give me a hand with this.

15:19.130 --> 15:19.460
Okay.

15:19.720 --> 15:20.380
Be careful.

15:21.460 --> 15:22.360
Come on, be careful.

15:22.360 --> 15:22.890
Careful.

15:24.000 --> 15:24.330
Good.

15:25.100 --> 15:26.500
Little Northeasterner!

15:26.790 --> 15:28.480
Get a room ready for this girl.

15:27.970 --> 15:31.720
[Registration Room]

15:30.770 --> 15:31.700
What's going on?

15:32.110 --> 15:33.490
What do you mean, "what's going on"?

15:33.490 --> 15:36.540
[Registration Room]

15:34.100 --> 15:35.860
From your hometown? Your classmate?

15:35.860 --> 15:37.660
The girl from the train station.

15:38.740 --> 15:39.750
So it's a series.

15:40.170 --> 15:42.300
Alright. What kind of room do you want?

15:43.550 --> 15:44.620
Same as his is fine.

15:44.890 --> 15:45.750
The 6-yuan one.

15:47.530 --> 15:48.700
Girls' rooms usually have 2

15:48.700 --> 15:49.290
to a room,

15:49.360 --> 15:50.290
or 3 at most.

15:50.550 --> 15:51.630
So there's no 6-yuan rate.

15:51.630 --> 15:52.490
It's all 8 yuan.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.240
Eight yuan?

15:56.580 --> 15:58.500
Didn't you say
that referrals from regular guests

15:58.500 --> 15:59.700
could get a discount?

16:02.410 --> 16:03.370
Referrals are

16:03.390 --> 16:04.720
definitely different.

16:04.790 --> 16:05.510
How about this?

16:05.510 --> 16:06.440
Um, you must be tired.

16:06.440 --> 16:07.320
Sit there and take a rest.

16:07.320 --> 16:08.720
The two of us need to talk.

16:10.610 --> 16:16.150
[Registration Room]

16:10.650 --> 16:11.710
Y-You go rest a bit.

16:18.270 --> 16:18.870
What's up?

16:20.840 --> 16:21.770
What do you mean?

16:21.960 --> 16:22.530
What? What's wrong?

16:22.530 --> 16:23.030
Well,

16:23.980 --> 16:25.710
are you paying the extra 2 yuan?

16:28.220 --> 16:29.880
This girl just got to Beijing.

16:30.200 --> 16:32.000
She had 2,000 yuan stolen.

16:32.220 --> 16:34.350
I'm helping her and seeing it through.

16:34.410 --> 16:35.750
I'm impressed, Mr. Xu.

16:35.790 --> 16:37.360
I didn't know you had it in you.

16:37.360 --> 16:38.670
You hooked up
as soon as you got to Beijing.

16:38.670 --> 16:39.870
Don't talk nonsense.

16:39.960 --> 16:41.160
It's helping others.

16:41.270 --> 16:42.270
Where's she from?

16:42.820 --> 16:43.350
Wenzhou.

16:43.700 --> 16:44.510
What's her name?

16:44.510 --> 16:45.150
Zhuang Zhuang.

16:45.150 --> 16:46.530
What's she doing in Beijing?

16:46.530 --> 16:47.170
Learning to sing.

16:47.170 --> 16:48.320
She says she wants to take an exam

16:48.320 --> 16:49.860
for a s-song and dance troupe.

16:49.860 --> 16:51.460
So how did she end up with you?

16:53.050 --> 16:54.340
I've told you so many times!

16:54.340 --> 16:54.960
We two have been

16:54.960 --> 16:56.760
to the police station together.

16:57.620 --> 17:00.010
She's really the one
from the train station?

17:00.010 --> 17:01.150
I have to ask clearly.

17:01.150 --> 17:02.790
What if she's a murderer or arsonist?

17:02.790 --> 17:04.310
I can't explain it if the police come.

17:04.310 --> 17:05.740
J-Just look at her.

17:05.810 --> 17:06.960
How could she be a murderer or arsonist?

17:06.960 --> 17:08.569
You're paying the 2 yuan, huh?

17:08.569 --> 17:10.369
But you two can't live together.

17:11.109 --> 17:12.369
What are you thinking?

17:12.810 --> 17:14.400
We'll live separately!

17:14.510 --> 17:15.839
Then what are you after?

17:17.940 --> 17:19.940
I... I just want you to earn more.

17:19.940 --> 17:21.290
What am I after?

17:21.670 --> 17:22.800
[Registration Room]

17:23.140 --> 17:24.040
Mr. Xu!

17:24.109 --> 17:25.710
Let me add a couple of things.

17:27.420 --> 17:28.770
Even though you're not living together,

17:28.770 --> 17:29.900
you can't make those kinds

17:29.900 --> 17:31.030
of improper noises.

17:31.350 --> 17:32.880
I'll give you some noises right now.

17:32.880 --> 17:33.760
Don't mess with me.

17:33.760 --> 17:34.460
Listen,

17:34.790 --> 17:35.570
if you lay a finger on me,

17:35.570 --> 17:36.980
I'll expose your ulterior motives

17:36.980 --> 17:37.770
to the public.

17:37.770 --> 17:38.570
-W-What?
-Dare you move?

17:38.570 --> 17:40.050
What ulterior motives do I have?

17:40.050 --> 17:41.270
Miss Zhuang Zhuang!

17:42.290 --> 17:44.110
You're Miss Zhuang Zhuang, right?

17:44.110 --> 17:45.170
Sorry for the wait.

17:45.350 --> 17:46.310
Let's see the room.

17:46.310 --> 17:48.090
Come check out the environment inside.

17:48.090 --> 17:48.660
Okay.

17:49.720 --> 17:50.180
Hi, Luo.

17:52.350 --> 17:54.060
I live in this room, 108.

17:57.640 --> 17:58.290
Can't believe you

17:58.290 --> 17:59.850
turned a basement into this.

17:59.850 --> 18:01.450
Girls' rooms are over there.

18:01.680 --> 18:03.340
D-Do you think it's too messy?

18:03.440 --> 18:05.090
No, I think it's great.

18:05.420 --> 18:06.180
When I was little,

18:06.180 --> 18:07.180
I really envied those

18:07.180 --> 18:08.310
who lived in dorms.

18:08.880 --> 18:09.790
I didn't expect

18:09.880 --> 18:10.660
someone as elegant as you

18:10.660 --> 18:11.990
to be so down-to-earth.

18:12.110 --> 18:13.840
If not, I wouldn't even be here.

18:16.960 --> 18:17.820
Anyone inside?

18:19.790 --> 18:20.680
I'm coming in!

18:28.510 --> 18:29.440
Come in, please.

18:32.230 --> 18:33.990
This bed is for an actress.

18:34.420 --> 18:35.550
For the sake of privacy,

18:35.550 --> 18:36.810
she took the outer bed.

18:36.960 --> 18:37.850
So you can have

18:37.880 --> 18:39.680
the best spot here by the window.

18:39.790 --> 18:40.700
Even though it's a basement,

18:40.700 --> 18:41.510
I can assure you that it's

18:41.510 --> 18:42.750
warm in winter and cool in summer.

18:42.750 --> 18:44.010
If you have your own bedding,

18:44.010 --> 18:44.810
use yours.

18:44.900 --> 18:45.940
If not, I have some ready for you.

18:45.940 --> 18:47.310
I have everything. I brought it with me.

18:47.310 --> 18:48.570
If you think it's okay,

18:48.770 --> 18:49.180
come upstairs

18:49.180 --> 18:50.050
to sign an agreement with me later.

18:50.050 --> 18:51.160
And then you can move in.

18:51.160 --> 18:51.990
I really like it.

18:51.990 --> 18:52.650
Brilliant.

18:52.960 --> 18:53.850
Let me show you

18:53.850 --> 18:54.660
the facilities.

18:54.660 --> 18:55.790
-Okay.
-Let me do it.

18:57.220 --> 18:58.680
That saves me the trouble.

18:59.180 --> 19:01.290
If you have any questions,
just ask Mr. Xu.

19:01.290 --> 19:02.150
I'm off to work.

19:03.330 --> 19:04.420
Thank you, sir!

19:06.140 --> 19:07.250
Didn't we pass by

19:07.250 --> 19:08.200
the washroom earlier?

19:08.200 --> 19:09.640
There's hot water and showers.

19:09.640 --> 19:10.720
You can use them anytime.

19:10.720 --> 19:11.780
And for cooking...

19:12.920 --> 19:14.530
You still have a bag upstairs!

19:14.530 --> 19:15.240
Um, sir...

19:17.550 --> 19:18.380
Mr. Xu.

19:20.500 --> 19:22.000
Thank you for recommending

19:22.000 --> 19:23.260
such an awesome place.

19:23.380 --> 19:24.380
Don't mention it.

19:25.290 --> 19:25.900
Well,

19:26.750 --> 19:27.680
about the money,

19:27.740 --> 19:28.980
if I use it to pay the deposit,

19:28.980 --> 19:30.160
can I pay you back in a couple of days?

19:30.160 --> 19:30.910
No rush!

19:31.250 --> 19:32.180
Really, no rush.

19:32.570 --> 19:34.180
Just don't make yourself
faint from hunger again.

19:34.180 --> 19:34.710
Besides,

19:34.720 --> 19:36.160
we'll be neighbors from now on.

19:36.160 --> 19:37.280
In half a month,

19:37.830 --> 19:39.510
1 month, or even 2 months,
it'll all be fine.

19:39.510 --> 19:40.840
It won't take that long.

19:40.880 --> 19:41.410
It won't.

19:44.010 --> 19:46.200
I'll tidy this place up, and it'll look

19:46.200 --> 19:47.050
totally different.

19:47.050 --> 19:48.980
I'll invite you to take a look then.

19:49.220 --> 19:49.570
Okay.

19:49.960 --> 19:50.940
T-Then you go ahead and tidy up.

19:50.940 --> 19:51.940
I'll get your bag.

19:52.660 --> 19:53.240
Mr. Xu.

19:54.900 --> 19:56.630
I really appreciate your help.

19:56.700 --> 19:57.810
Don't mention it.

19:57.890 --> 19:59.130
Just settle in.

20:17.640 --> 20:19.240
You got this, Zhuang Zhuang.

20:38.920 --> 20:42.250
"May you enjoy your stay here."

20:51.940 --> 20:52.420
Hello.

20:52.960 --> 20:54.020
I'm Zhuang Zhuang.

20:59.920 --> 21:01.120
Who let you live here?

21:01.810 --> 21:02.410
The owner.

21:02.570 --> 21:03.850
He said this room

21:04.110 --> 21:06.770
wouldn't have anyone else,
so I decided to stay here.

21:06.770 --> 21:08.160
Why don't you go ask him?

21:08.500 --> 21:09.510
I paid, too.

21:20.530 --> 21:21.510
You promised to give me

21:21.510 --> 21:22.610
a single room this morning!

21:22.610 --> 21:24.050
But now someone else has moved in!

21:24.050 --> 21:25.020
What do you mean?

21:25.290 --> 21:26.730
Come out here and explain!

21:26.730 --> 21:29.190
[Registration Room]

21:32.020 --> 21:39.720
[Registration Room]

21:34.790 --> 21:35.240
Miss,

21:35.550 --> 21:36.150
calm down.

21:36.380 --> 21:37.240
Don't be angry.

21:37.790 --> 21:38.740
This morning,

21:38.900 --> 21:40.770
your room was indeed a single.

21:41.270 --> 21:42.200
But now it's not.

21:42.220 --> 21:43.350
Someone else arrived.

21:43.350 --> 21:44.950
I couldn't just kick her out.

21:45.350 --> 21:46.000
The main thing is,

21:46.000 --> 21:47.630
our location is too good.

21:47.740 --> 21:48.940
Business is booming.

21:49.400 --> 21:50.720
There isn't a single bed left.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.980
I really had no choice.

21:51.980 --> 21:52.980
You big liar!

21:53.180 --> 21:54.240
This is a shady inn!

21:54.610 --> 21:55.540
I'm not staying.

21:55.880 --> 21:57.030
How did my place become

21:57.030 --> 21:58.180
a shady inn?

21:58.500 --> 22:00.630
You've been reading too many scripts.

22:01.000 --> 22:01.850
If you stay here,

22:01.850 --> 22:03.580
I can't promise anything else,

22:03.850 --> 22:06.310
but I can definitely
guarantee your safety.

22:06.400 --> 22:07.740
Also, I don't just put

22:07.740 --> 22:09.000
anyone in your room.

22:09.070 --> 22:10.220
Sketchy people

22:10.270 --> 22:10.850
can't even get into

22:10.850 --> 22:12.300
this place.

22:12.480 --> 22:13.310
Besides,

22:13.740 --> 22:15.960
you'll definitely be filming later.

22:16.030 --> 22:16.900
You'll be on set.

22:16.900 --> 22:18.160
You're an actress.

22:18.720 --> 22:19.530
This is just a place

22:19.530 --> 22:20.660
to store your stuff.

22:21.200 --> 22:21.600
Right?

22:22.250 --> 22:23.450
That's in the future.

22:23.770 --> 22:25.350
I'm going to be a star.

22:26.160 --> 22:26.900
How can I let others

22:26.900 --> 22:27.910
see my privacy?

22:28.380 --> 22:28.780
Right.

22:29.720 --> 22:30.500
Privacy...

22:30.640 --> 22:31.050
Look.

22:31.070 --> 22:31.680
Little Northeasterner.

22:31.680 --> 22:32.680
We common folk...

22:33.810 --> 22:35.340
Don't say I didn't warn you.

22:35.700 --> 22:37.000
A bright star is

22:37.000 --> 22:38.110
about to rise.

22:38.160 --> 22:39.350
If you destroy her,

22:39.790 --> 22:41.110
you'll be a sinner.

22:41.350 --> 22:42.480
I won't forgive you.

22:43.810 --> 22:44.530
Well, Mr. Tao.

22:44.530 --> 22:45.130
We are just

22:45.550 --> 22:46.740
discussing our business.

22:46.740 --> 22:48.550
Let's talk later if you need something.

22:48.550 --> 22:49.030
I know.

22:50.720 --> 22:52.050
I'm seeing an injustice

22:52.440 --> 22:53.770
and stepping in to help.

22:54.090 --> 22:55.220
One person in her room,

22:55.220 --> 22:55.960
one person in mine.

22:55.960 --> 22:57.270
Two issues become one.

22:57.530 --> 22:58.630
Can you solve it?

23:01.730 --> 23:02.310
Girl,

23:03.110 --> 23:03.940
leave this matter

23:03.940 --> 23:04.610
to me.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.460
Don't cry, don't be upset.

23:06.480 --> 23:07.520
I'll handle it.

23:07.830 --> 23:09.430
Just make do for 2 days, okay?

23:10.810 --> 23:12.610
If it weren't so close to the set,

23:13.010 --> 23:14.940
I wouldn't settle for a single day.

23:16.250 --> 23:16.750
Right.

23:17.160 --> 23:18.960
We won't settle for a single day.

23:19.680 --> 23:20.730
What are you going to do?

23:20.730 --> 23:21.590
Give me an explanation.

23:21.590 --> 23:22.810
Little Northeasterner,

23:22.810 --> 23:24.050
the new guy in our room

23:24.610 --> 23:26.470
really doesn't follow the rules.

23:26.480 --> 23:27.680
That's not Room 108's rule.

23:27.680 --> 23:29.680
That's the rule at Seasons Change Hotel.

23:29.680 --> 23:30.880
Everyone is watching.

23:30.880 --> 23:31.220
Right?

23:31.220 --> 23:31.700
If a place

23:31.700 --> 23:32.430
doesn't have rules,

23:32.430 --> 23:34.430
no one can live here forever, right?

23:34.640 --> 23:35.440
What's wrong?

23:36.750 --> 23:37.940
Perfect. Zongbao is back.

23:37.940 --> 23:38.980
-Come on.
-What’s wrong?

23:38.980 --> 23:40.810
Give the three of us an explanation today.

23:40.810 --> 23:42.420
What? What explanation?

23:44.740 --> 23:45.570
Gentlemen.

23:45.790 --> 23:47.320
I'll give you a suggestion.

23:47.480 --> 23:49.010
Each of you

23:49.090 --> 23:50.330
pays an extra 2 yuan a day

23:50.330 --> 23:51.560
to book

23:51.590 --> 23:52.590
the remaining bed.

23:52.590 --> 23:54.270
If I bring anyone else in,

23:54.740 --> 23:55.680
I'm a bastard.

23:55.740 --> 23:56.270
Deal?

23:56.720 --> 23:58.490
Wait. What are you doing?

23:58.610 --> 24:00.270
I have to pay extra?

24:00.330 --> 24:02.460
Wouldn't I be working for nothing all day?

24:02.460 --> 24:03.700
In your room,

24:04.250 --> 24:04.980
someone moves in,

24:04.980 --> 24:06.070
and you squeeze them out.

24:06.070 --> 24:06.720
Someone moves in,

24:06.720 --> 24:08.120
and you squeeze them out.

24:08.240 --> 24:09.160
Am I supposed to run a business

24:09.160 --> 24:10.050
or not?

24:10.550 --> 24:11.150
Everyone.

24:11.460 --> 24:12.720
You're all here today.

24:12.960 --> 24:14.220
Let me make this clear.

24:15.110 --> 24:16.240
If you think

24:16.310 --> 24:17.810
the person living in your room

24:17.810 --> 24:19.640
is an eyesore and want them out,

24:20.070 --> 24:21.320
pay for the bed.

24:21.750 --> 24:23.020
I won't

24:23.460 --> 24:24.270
say a word.

24:53.420 --> 24:58.130
[East Shore Club]

25:07.570 --> 25:09.970
[East Shore]

25:29.010 --> 25:29.470
Thanks.

25:45.680 --> 25:46.290
Buddy,

25:47.740 --> 25:49.400
I've held my tongue for 2 days.

25:50.290 --> 25:51.820
We're painting an archway.

25:51.830 --> 25:52.560
That blue...

25:52.590 --> 25:53.920
we can't be this sloppy.

25:54.070 --> 25:55.070
For the outlines,

25:55.070 --> 25:56.180
you need solid color.

25:56.180 --> 25:57.740
You have to use first-grade indigo.

25:57.740 --> 25:58.030
Right?

25:58.030 --> 25:59.070
For the center and background,

25:59.070 --> 26:00.180
shouldn't you use second-grade indigo?

26:00.180 --> 26:01.810
Then for the shading and details,

26:01.810 --> 26:03.180
you need third-grade indigo.

26:03.180 --> 26:04.380
Our ancestors passed this down.

26:04.380 --> 26:05.720
This is how archways should be painted.

26:05.720 --> 26:07.110
So after centuries of wind and sun,

26:07.110 --> 26:08.110
the base color remains.

26:08.110 --> 26:09.850
The Forbidden City,
Summer Palace, the Imperial College...

26:09.850 --> 26:11.110
they're all like this.

26:11.420 --> 26:12.500
I'm an oil painter,

26:12.500 --> 26:13.610
and even I know this.

26:13.610 --> 26:14.570
If we paint it like this...

26:14.570 --> 26:15.240
Man,

26:15.980 --> 26:17.400
we've stooped to painting this.

26:17.400 --> 26:18.660
Why are you so serious?

26:18.850 --> 26:20.100
It's just a job.

26:20.400 --> 26:22.180
I just consider myself a house painter.

26:22.180 --> 26:23.250
Just do your own work.

26:23.250 --> 26:24.110
Leave me alone.

26:24.830 --> 26:26.430
You're not the one paying me.

26:30.210 --> 26:33.070
[Seasons Change Hotel]

26:43.250 --> 26:44.250
I'm done reading.

26:58.720 --> 27:00.160
Let me make this clear first.

27:00.160 --> 27:01.250
I'm an actress.

27:01.880 --> 27:03.350
If I get the itch to act,

27:03.940 --> 27:04.790
in the middle of the night,

27:04.790 --> 27:06.120
I might perform a scene.

27:06.850 --> 27:07.780
Act all you want.

27:10.290 --> 27:12.010
Let me be clearer.

27:14.110 --> 27:15.030
In a few days,

27:16.140 --> 27:18.100
I'm playing a brutal killer.

27:18.740 --> 27:20.270
If I get too into character,

27:20.460 --> 27:22.260
I might lose touch with reality.

27:22.660 --> 27:24.790
Then you'd better keep them separate.

27:24.960 --> 27:26.220
Otherwise, the police

27:26.250 --> 27:27.450
will have to help you.

27:27.590 --> 27:28.280
I still

27:28.550 --> 27:29.890
suggest you move out

27:29.960 --> 27:30.960
for your own sake.

27:31.050 --> 27:32.180
If...

27:34.500 --> 27:35.720
You'll be in trouble.

27:41.090 --> 27:43.110
As for my books and magazines,

27:43.420 --> 27:44.950
you can read them whenever.

27:45.140 --> 27:46.470
But don't get them dirty

27:46.790 --> 27:47.920
or crease the pages.

27:53.700 --> 27:54.900
When I become famous,

27:55.290 --> 27:57.150
I'll be the star of this magazine.

27:57.330 --> 27:58.750
I'll give you an autograph then.

27:58.750 --> 28:00.550
Don't make me wait until I'm old.

28:09.980 --> 28:10.640
What music?

28:11.220 --> 28:12.010
What music?

28:12.310 --> 28:13.370
What opportunity?

28:13.810 --> 28:14.870
What opportunity?

28:15.770 --> 28:16.790
What...

28:17.530 --> 28:19.180
What opportunity?

28:27.840 --> 28:29.350
Taking over the nest.

28:29.660 --> 28:31.460
You've only been here a few days,

28:32.030 --> 28:34.180
and you're already acting like the boss.

28:34.180 --> 28:35.770
You shouldn't be so selfish.

28:35.770 --> 28:37.460
You have to leave yourself a way out.

28:37.460 --> 28:39.010
You guys weren't here just now.

28:39.010 --> 28:40.610
I was afraid the oscillating fan

28:40.610 --> 28:41.610
was just blowing air for nothing.

28:41.610 --> 28:42.960
Do you believe that yourself?

28:42.960 --> 28:43.890
A big guy like me—

28:43.960 --> 28:45.360
didn't you see me come in?

28:45.980 --> 28:48.040
Didn't you see me standing by the fan?

28:48.590 --> 28:50.510
Then let me salute you.

28:56.530 --> 28:57.990
We're all a bunch of moles,

28:58.010 --> 28:59.060
living in a cave.

28:59.250 --> 29:00.180
You have to learn

29:00.500 --> 29:01.980
to share the breeze.

29:02.480 --> 29:03.090
Well said.

29:04.400 --> 29:05.260
A bunch of moles

29:05.480 --> 29:06.540
living in a cave...

29:07.480 --> 29:09.830
Living just like moles.

29:11.250 --> 29:13.190
Didn't you, the mole, say we should

29:13.350 --> 29:14.350
share the breeze?

29:16.420 --> 29:18.020
Living like moles.

29:18.160 --> 29:19.220
Your share of the breeze, mole,

29:19.220 --> 29:20.050
you already

29:20.550 --> 29:21.920
finished enjoying it.

29:26.090 --> 29:27.590
Living like moles.

29:36.420 --> 29:37.810
That little thing of yours

29:37.810 --> 29:38.670
is pretty cute,

29:39.640 --> 29:41.090
but it's a lot of trouble.

29:41.200 --> 29:42.660
If you don't keep it clean,

29:42.830 --> 29:44.110
it spreads germs easily.

29:44.110 --> 29:45.220
Don't talk nonsense.

29:45.220 --> 29:46.280
He can understand.

29:46.460 --> 29:47.920
He's my son, Cao Xiaosong.

29:48.570 --> 29:49.570
I was just saying.

29:49.680 --> 29:50.940
It's for your own good.

29:51.900 --> 29:52.790
We're living in a place like this,

29:52.790 --> 29:54.050
why be so fussy?

29:54.240 --> 29:55.440
Talking about germs.

29:55.700 --> 29:56.100
You...

29:56.380 --> 29:58.030
If you're so capable,
go live in a big hotel.

29:58.030 --> 29:58.960
Germs, my foot.

29:59.610 --> 30:00.310
Cao.

30:01.070 --> 30:01.800
You're back.

30:01.960 --> 30:02.330
Zongbao.

30:02.330 --> 30:02.860
Zongbao.

30:04.140 --> 30:05.230
Writing a letter?

30:06.310 --> 30:07.710
I'm revising the script.

30:08.480 --> 30:09.740
Revising the script?

30:12.790 --> 30:13.500
I gotta say,

30:14.220 --> 30:16.480
your handwriting is really impressive.

30:19.980 --> 30:20.380
Bro,

30:21.380 --> 30:22.640
you go hustle
the film studio all the time.

30:22.640 --> 30:24.440
Have you heard of Director Weng?

30:24.480 --> 30:25.550
In our line of work,

30:25.550 --> 30:26.480
who doesn't know

30:26.850 --> 30:27.920
Director Weng?

30:31.050 --> 30:33.850
Are you writing a script for him?

30:37.370 --> 30:39.180
[To Director Weng]

30:40.960 --> 30:43.830
So you're a professional screenwriter.

30:45.910 --> 30:51.670
[Jinhai Seafood Processing Plant Award]

30:49.460 --> 30:50.250
Semi, semi.

30:51.030 --> 30:52.230
Semi-professional.

30:53.260 --> 30:54.180
That works too.

30:54.290 --> 30:56.120
So half of it is professional.

30:56.770 --> 30:59.970
So, about your script...

31:00.460 --> 31:02.980
Is there a role I can play?

31:05.980 --> 31:07.720
The thing is, I don't know you very well.

31:07.720 --> 31:08.330
I don't know what...

31:08.330 --> 31:08.850
It's okay.

31:08.850 --> 31:09.880
No problem.

31:10.270 --> 31:10.740
Come.

31:11.440 --> 31:13.090
Sit, sit. Come.

31:13.640 --> 31:15.770
Let's get to know each other properly.

31:16.090 --> 31:17.740
I'm Guo Zongbao.

31:18.240 --> 31:19.840
My ancestral home is He'nan.

31:20.310 --> 31:22.500
My debut work...

31:22.810 --> 31:25.010
was the new version of

31:25.900 --> 31:27.480
Plain Ranger Team.

31:27.920 --> 31:30.550
I played the captain.

31:31.330 --> 31:32.730
You played Li Xiangyang?

31:33.110 --> 31:33.350
No.

31:33.350 --> 31:35.900
That's the guerrilla captain.

31:35.980 --> 31:38.310
I was the district squad captain.

31:39.790 --> 31:41.030
Who are you kidding?

31:42.140 --> 31:43.340
You're just an extra.

31:43.570 --> 31:44.960
What extra?

31:45.160 --> 31:46.790
A guest actor.

31:47.350 --> 31:48.440
I even had lines.

31:48.900 --> 31:50.100
I said, "Charge!"

31:50.330 --> 31:51.640
Those big stars

31:51.680 --> 31:52.790
ran like rabbits.

31:52.940 --> 31:54.870
Whoosh, whoosh! They charged out.

31:55.220 --> 31:56.610
Let me show you stills.

32:04.850 --> 32:05.180
Here.

32:05.900 --> 32:06.500
That's me.

32:06.880 --> 32:08.010
I was thin back then.

32:08.350 --> 32:09.670
Beijing puts meat on your bones.

32:09.030 --> 32:10.760
[1989 Commemoration]

32:10.420 --> 32:11.820
The director told me,

32:12.480 --> 32:13.540
my performance was

32:13.570 --> 32:15.220
relaxed yet powerful.

32:16.210 --> 32:17.840
I have standards

32:18.110 --> 32:19.580
for my own acting.

32:20.270 --> 32:21.000
Bro,

32:21.350 --> 32:22.950
write me a role

32:22.980 --> 32:24.810
that lets me surpass myself.

32:25.030 --> 32:25.940
Yeah, right!

32:28.420 --> 32:28.990
Zongbao.

32:29.700 --> 32:31.700
When Liangliang comes back and sees

32:31.980 --> 32:32.980
you've defected,

32:33.740 --> 32:34.750
he'll smack you.

32:38.250 --> 32:39.330
Besides, can't you see

32:39.330 --> 32:40.350
he's not interested in you?

32:40.350 --> 32:40.960
You're kissing

32:40.960 --> 32:42.490
-up to him...
-Don’t worry.

32:43.220 --> 32:44.980
I've noted your request.

32:45.310 --> 32:46.440
I'll keep it in mind.

32:46.590 --> 32:47.570
Thanks.

32:48.090 --> 32:50.000
Take it to heart.

32:50.240 --> 32:50.970
Don't worry.

32:51.140 --> 32:52.030
Alright then.

32:52.440 --> 32:52.940
Well,

32:53.180 --> 32:54.330
keep revising.

32:54.530 --> 32:56.390
I've been around the film studio.

32:56.490 --> 32:57.180
I know.

32:57.380 --> 32:58.660
Screenwriting

32:58.830 --> 32:59.640
isn't easy.

33:00.330 --> 33:01.480
Writing one

33:02.400 --> 33:03.540
takes 2 or 3 years.

33:04.240 --> 33:06.640
If things go wrong, 3 to 5 years.

33:07.380 --> 33:10.050
Worst case, 10 years.

33:11.050 --> 33:12.250
No matter what you do,

33:12.440 --> 33:13.460
life is tough,

33:13.920 --> 33:15.320
and money is hard to earn.

33:16.880 --> 33:18.210
Some even take 10 years?

33:23.250 --> 33:24.110
Let me tell you,

33:24.110 --> 33:24.970
you must hold in

33:24.980 --> 33:25.850
that dialect of yours.

33:25.850 --> 33:27.090
Don't let it slip out. Do you hear me?

33:27.090 --> 33:28.220
Okay, Director Cui.

33:28.440 --> 33:28.960
And,

33:29.420 --> 33:30.290
you must relax.

33:30.610 --> 33:31.610
Don't be nervous.

33:32.330 --> 33:33.090
Clear your mind.

33:33.090 --> 33:33.880
And immerse yourself

33:33.880 --> 33:34.590
in the role.

33:35.030 --> 33:36.230
Don't worry, Mr. Cui.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.400
I'm a professional.

33:37.400 --> 33:39.260
Good. Confidence is a good thing.

33:39.960 --> 33:41.110
The assistant casting director here

33:41.110 --> 33:42.010
is a buddy of mine.

33:42.010 --> 33:43.050
I've put in a good word.

33:43.050 --> 33:44.510
Just focus on your acting.

33:44.700 --> 33:45.740
Thank you, Mr. Cui.

33:45.740 --> 33:46.740
Don't mention it.

33:47.110 --> 33:48.590
Your teacher is my buddy too.

33:48.590 --> 33:48.960
Go on.

33:51.940 --> 33:55.160
[Love Debt Filming Team]

33:53.920 --> 33:54.660
Come in.

33:59.660 --> 34:00.750
A girl from Huzhou.

34:01.440 --> 34:02.210
Hello, Director.

34:01.590 --> 34:08.090
[Character settings]

34:02.500 --> 34:03.140
Hello.

34:03.200 --> 34:04.440
I... I am Shen Ranran.

34:06.000 --> 34:07.070
Shen Ranran.

34:08.920 --> 34:10.360
Huzhou, Zhejiang.

34:11.880 --> 34:13.760
You were in 2 movies.

34:15.670 --> 34:17.199
When will they be released?

34:17.920 --> 34:19.050
I don't know yet.

34:21.500 --> 34:23.230
No wonder I haven't seen them.

34:24.110 --> 34:25.760
I heard she's good.

34:27.880 --> 34:28.610
You heard?

34:29.320 --> 34:30.780
Yes.

34:32.380 --> 34:32.780
Okay.

34:34.710 --> 34:35.530
Do you know each other?

34:35.530 --> 34:36.730
Or have you worked together?

34:36.730 --> 34:37.150
No.

34:37.570 --> 34:39.630
Assistant Director Cui introduced her.

34:39.630 --> 34:40.159
Alright.

34:40.610 --> 34:41.360
Pick a scene.

34:42.730 --> 34:43.610
Let's see what you've got.

34:43.590 --> 34:50.650
[Character settings]

34:44.510 --> 34:44.940
Okay.

34:47.880 --> 34:48.810
Come on, Ranran.

34:49.500 --> 34:50.710
I've marked it for you.

34:50.710 --> 34:52.940
You all think you're such big shots, huh?

34:52.940 --> 34:54.440
You're being so picky.

34:55.130 --> 34:55.980
Let me tell you,

34:55.980 --> 34:57.860
you're just fillers. Understand?

34:57.860 --> 34:59.170
But not for free.

34:59.340 --> 35:00.270
You'll get paid.

35:00.480 --> 35:02.030
Those I picked, follow me.

35:02.360 --> 35:03.510
Me! Me! Me!

35:03.510 --> 35:04.340
You, you.

35:04.780 --> 35:05.460
You, you.

35:05.630 --> 35:06.230
That girl.

35:06.650 --> 35:07.450
Get on the bus.

35:07.960 --> 35:09.960
We only need this many people today.

35:10.010 --> 35:11.400
Go find work elsewhere.

35:11.800 --> 35:12.400
Clear out.

35:13.070 --> 35:13.730
Move along.

35:15.610 --> 35:16.340
I'm leaving.

35:16.650 --> 35:17.650
See you tomorrow.

35:17.840 --> 35:18.340
Take care.

35:18.340 --> 35:18.780
Okay.

35:20.840 --> 35:21.640
Director Wei.

35:23.590 --> 35:25.050
You've been working hard.

35:25.610 --> 35:27.210
Look at all this sweat. Here.

35:27.210 --> 35:28.150
Here, sit, sit.

35:28.210 --> 35:29.410
Sit for a while. Here.

35:29.440 --> 35:30.210
Let me cover it.

35:30.210 --> 35:31.170
It's dirty.

35:31.550 --> 35:32.410
Here, sit down.

35:32.590 --> 35:33.250
Please sit.

35:33.510 --> 35:34.510
Go away.

35:35.110 --> 35:35.780
I... I...

35:36.010 --> 35:38.630
I brought you breakfast.

35:38.900 --> 35:39.700
This pancake.

35:40.550 --> 35:41.590
-Stop.
-It’s still hot.

35:41.590 --> 35:42.650
I don't need your pancake.

35:42.650 --> 35:43.930
I don't need it.

35:44.000 --> 35:45.110
I've been working all morning.

35:45.110 --> 35:46.050
I'm already fired up enough.

35:46.050 --> 35:46.910
Don't choke me.

35:47.000 --> 35:47.600
It's okay.

35:48.030 --> 35:49.890
I have something to cool you down.

35:50.150 --> 35:51.010
Mung bean soup.

35:51.230 --> 35:51.570
Here.

35:53.320 --> 35:54.250
I made it myself.

35:55.300 --> 35:56.630
It's chilled. Drink up.

36:01.590 --> 36:03.000
There aren't many roles with lines.

36:03.000 --> 36:03.590
Really?

36:04.510 --> 36:05.800
Watch repair shop.

36:07.600 --> 36:09.350
Grain store counter.

36:10.260 --> 36:12.450
[The Last Palace Romance]

36:11.230 --> 36:12.360
The Last...

36:12.940 --> 36:13.280
This one.

36:13.280 --> 36:13.940
The Last...

36:15.650 --> 36:16.850
You're the right age.

36:17.440 --> 36:18.010
Really?

36:22.780 --> 36:23.760
The Emperor?

36:24.010 --> 36:25.920
What are you thinking? Emperor?

36:26.800 --> 36:27.170
Eu...

36:27.780 --> 36:28.300
Eunuch.

36:30.110 --> 36:31.070
The Head Eunuch.

36:31.650 --> 36:33.650
Hanging around the Emperor all day.

36:33.650 --> 36:34.650
The camera will catch your ear,

36:34.650 --> 36:35.650
or half your face.

36:35.710 --> 36:37.040
Isn't that good enough?

36:38.150 --> 36:38.480
Okay.

36:39.460 --> 36:40.320
That works too.

36:40.460 --> 36:41.420
You're right.

36:42.260 --> 36:44.120
If I can become

36:44.210 --> 36:45.870
an expert at playing eunuchs,

36:46.300 --> 36:47.320
then my big break

36:47.530 --> 36:48.440
won't be far off.

36:48.440 --> 36:49.800
5:30 tomorrow morning.

36:49.880 --> 36:50.540
Right here.

36:51.260 --> 36:51.790
Yes, sir.

36:53.360 --> 36:58.210
Mom told me when I was little,

36:57.440 --> 37:00.720
[All for the children]

36:58.400 --> 37:03.260
the sea is my hometown.

37:03.550 --> 37:08.010
Born by the sea.

37:08.190 --> 37:12.230
Grew up in the sea.

37:12.340 --> 37:13.590
Okay, that's enough.

37:14.280 --> 37:15.960
Your singing is quite good.

37:16.230 --> 37:18.490
But do you have any teaching experience?

37:18.550 --> 37:19.710
I went to a teachers' college.

37:19.710 --> 37:21.360
I taught children back in my hometown.

37:21.360 --> 37:23.220
You know music theory too, right?

37:23.340 --> 37:25.320
Let's try a class first.

37:25.800 --> 37:26.920
Great. Thank you.

37:27.820 --> 37:28.690
May I ask

37:28.690 --> 37:30.220
what the monthly salary is?

37:33.380 --> 37:35.380
Isn't it a bit early to ask that?

37:37.050 --> 37:37.760
Excuse me.

37:47.250 --> 37:48.580
There's another piece.

37:50.980 --> 37:52.430
Wang, you've got a job?

37:52.000 --> 37:55.350
[Bicycle Repair]

37:53.090 --> 37:55.070
There's plenty of work.
People are lining up.

37:55.070 --> 37:56.670
Lining up. Business is good.

37:57.080 --> 37:58.630
I picked up 2 pieces of wire.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.900
I'll go get my tools.

38:01.900 --> 38:03.360
You're just fixing range hoods.

38:03.360 --> 38:05.220
Why are you acting all secretive?

38:06.280 --> 38:08.540
There is no shame in working for a living.

38:09.070 --> 38:10.280
My roommates

38:10.360 --> 38:12.330
only know I'm an actor.

38:12.610 --> 38:14.540
So what role did you play recently?

38:14.590 --> 38:16.520
I played a high-ranking official.

38:17.760 --> 38:19.010
A high-ranking official?

38:19.010 --> 38:20.820
A really high-ranking official.

38:20.820 --> 38:21.780
That's great.

38:22.610 --> 38:23.710
Great.

38:28.460 --> 38:32.200
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

38:29.230 --> 38:30.030
Wait a minute.

38:30.110 --> 38:30.460
What?

38:30.730 --> 38:31.880
That...

38:31.980 --> 38:33.780
really high-ranking official.

38:34.010 --> 38:35.610
What kind of official was it?

38:38.260 --> 38:39.160
A eunuch.

38:40.590 --> 38:43.400
Well, a eunuch counts as an official?

38:44.690 --> 38:45.760
A eunuch is an official?

38:45.760 --> 38:49.150
Repairing range hoods!

38:49.860 --> 38:52.710
Unclogging drains!

38:54.360 --> 38:58.950
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

38:56.130 --> 38:58.170
Be careful. Slow down.

38:58.340 --> 39:01.200
Repairing range hoods!

39:01.280 --> 39:03.460
Unclogging drains!

39:03.520 --> 39:05.710
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

39:04.630 --> 39:05.920
Excuse me.

39:06.230 --> 39:06.760
Thanks.

39:07.210 --> 39:11.690
Ah, ah, ah...

39:12.980 --> 39:17.150
Ribbit, ribbit, ribbit...

39:17.300 --> 39:18.420
Is that your child?

39:18.650 --> 39:20.550
My youngest son has always been naughty.

39:20.550 --> 39:21.860
He looks well-behaved.

39:21.860 --> 39:22.380
Not at all.

39:22.380 --> 39:23.170
Be serious.

39:23.170 --> 39:23.940
He's a handful.

39:23.940 --> 39:25.200
Kids are all like that.

39:25.730 --> 39:27.330
He makes friends instantly.

39:27.960 --> 39:28.420
Come on.

39:29.320 --> 39:29.920
Come here.

39:31.070 --> 39:32.100
What's your name?

39:32.130 --> 39:34.050
My name is Frog. Ribbit, ribbit.

39:35.570 --> 39:36.960
You mean the water kid
from Calabash Brothers

39:36.960 --> 39:38.240
—the fifth one?

39:38.460 --> 39:38.900
Yes.

39:39.360 --> 39:40.560
Then you're amazing.

39:40.610 --> 39:42.610
You can suck in water and spit it out.

39:43.800 --> 39:44.730
When the water kid sucks in water,

39:44.730 --> 39:46.330
where does it go? Do you know?

39:46.460 --> 39:47.040
Here.

39:48.000 --> 39:48.950
Let me see.

39:49.400 --> 39:50.420
Show me how you suck it in.

39:50.420 --> 39:51.000
Okay?

39:51.130 --> 39:51.460
Okay.

39:51.460 --> 39:53.800
Come on. 1, 2, 3. Suck.

39:55.590 --> 39:59.380
Ah, ah, ah...

39:59.380 --> 40:01.390
Awesome. Well done.

40:02.010 --> 40:03.810
Show them how it's done. Come on.

40:05.340 --> 40:06.940
This teacher is pretty good.

40:07.320 --> 40:08.070
We just hired her.

40:08.070 --> 40:08.670
She's new?

40:08.800 --> 40:09.940
Did he do a good job? Right.

40:09.940 --> 40:10.510
Good.

40:10.510 --> 40:11.910
Let's give him a big hand.

40:12.110 --> 40:12.690
Awesome.

40:12.840 --> 40:13.730
Come on, go back to your seat.

40:13.730 --> 40:15.460
Let's do it all together, okay?

40:15.780 --> 40:16.730
Okay.

40:16.820 --> 40:17.710
She's a really good teacher.

40:17.710 --> 40:18.440
Pretty good.

40:18.980 --> 40:19.530
Come on.

40:21.630 --> 40:26.550
Ah, ah, ah...

40:28.500 --> 40:30.210
The waves surge,

40:30.320 --> 40:33.610
drifting with me everywhere.

40:35.570 --> 40:36.800
You got good news?

40:36.960 --> 40:37.840
So childish.

40:39.070 --> 40:40.270
You're even singing.

40:41.070 --> 40:43.500
I finally found a job today.

40:45.190 --> 40:46.860
But I won't get paid
until the end of the month.

40:46.860 --> 40:48.480
I'll pay you back right away then.

40:48.480 --> 40:49.280
I told you,

40:49.340 --> 40:50.940
no need to rush to pay me back.

40:51.050 --> 40:52.510
I'm not that short on cash.

40:53.010 --> 40:54.810
But finding a job is a good thing.

40:55.190 --> 40:57.890
It's the first step
to finding your footing.

40:59.760 --> 41:01.220
I'm nowhere near that yet.

41:01.730 --> 41:03.380
At best,

41:06.820 --> 41:08.080
I'm just on my tiptoes.

41:09.030 --> 41:09.830
Here, douzhi.

41:11.070 --> 41:13.150
So this is Beijing douzhi.

41:13.170 --> 41:14.570
Wait. You smell it first.

41:23.500 --> 41:24.500
Like stinky tofu.

41:24.500 --> 41:26.090
Smells stinky, tastes good.

41:26.090 --> 41:26.550
Really?

41:40.460 --> 41:41.360
A real hero takes 3 sips.

41:41.360 --> 41:42.360
I'll drink first.

41:49.210 --> 41:50.460
No, no, no. Yours...

41:50.760 --> 41:51.620
Let me smell it.

42:07.430 --> 42:07.960
How is it?

42:12.820 --> 42:14.220
Can you singing students

42:14.800 --> 42:16.050
turn off your sense of taste?

42:16.050 --> 42:17.510
Can't you taste anything?

42:18.570 --> 42:19.230
Keep going.

42:33.500 --> 42:35.630
Are you spitting it out or drinking it?

42:37.690 --> 42:38.290
It's good.

42:39.500 --> 42:40.100
It's good?

42:40.190 --> 42:40.690
It's good.

42:40.690 --> 42:41.440
Have another bowl.

42:41.440 --> 42:41.760
No.

42:42.170 --> 42:42.780
I'll get you another bowl.

42:42.780 --> 42:44.130
No, don't.

42:44.230 --> 42:45.050
I'm full.

42:48.090 --> 42:49.070
Didn't you say it was good?
